'''三甲基碘硅烷'''，又称'''三甲基碘化硅'''或 '''TMSI'''，是一种[[有机硅化合物|有机硅化合物]]，化学式为(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>SiI。它在室温下是一种无色挥发性液体。

==制备==
三甲基碘硅烷可以由[[六甲基乙硅烷|六甲基乙硅烷]]和[[碘|碘]]单质反应而成。<ref name="Olah">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/0040-4020(82)87002-6 | title= Iodotrimethylsilane—a versatile synthetic reagent| year = 1982 | last1 = Olah | first1 = G | last2 = Narang | first2 = S. C. | journal = Tetrahedron | volume = 38 | issue = 15 | pages = 2225}}</ref> 它也可以由[[六甲基二硅氧烷|六甲基二硅氧烷]]和[[三碘化铝|三碘化铝]]的反应生成：<ref name="Olah" /><ref>{{OrgSynth | collvol = 6 | collvolpages = 353 | year = 1988 | title = Cleavage of Methyl Ethers with Iodotrimethylsilane: Cyclohexanol from Cyclohexyl Methyl Ether | author1 = [[Michael_E._Jung|Michael E. Jung]] | author2 = Mark A. Lyster | prep = cv6p0353}}</ref>
: TMS-TMS + I<sub>2</sub> → 2 TMSI (TMS = (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>Si)
: 3 TMS-O-TMS + 2 AlI<sub>3</sub> → 6 TMSI + Al<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>

==应用==
三甲基碘硅烷可以给[[醇|醇]]类（ROH）引入[[三甲基硅基|三甲基硅基]]：

:R-OH + TMSI → R-OTMS + HI

由于所得的[[硅醚|硅醚]]比原料（醇）的挥发性更大，因此这种类型的反应对于[[气相色谱|气相色谱]]分析可能有用。 <ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chem.agilent.com/Library/applications/gcms59_opiates_urine.pdf | title = GC/MS Analysis for Morphine and Other Opiates in Urine }}{{Dead link}}</ref> 但是，对于制备本体三甲基硅烷基卤的材料，由于[[三甲基氯硅烷|三甲基氯硅烷]]的成本较低，因此是优选的。

TMSI会和[[醚|醚]]（ROR′）反应，形成[[碘代烃|碘代烃]]和三甲基硅基醚（ROSiMe<sub>3</sub>），其水解可以生成醇。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Michael E. Jung |author2=Mark A. Lyster | title = Quantitative dealkylation of alkyl ethers via treatment with trimethylsilyl iodide. A new method for ether hydrolysis | journal = [[Journal_of_Organic_Chemistry|J. Org. Chem.]] | volume = 42 |issue=23 | year = 1977 | pages = 3761–3764 | doi = 10.1021/jo00443a033}}</ref>

三甲基碘硅烷可以用来移除[[叔丁氧羰基|叔丁氧羰基]]，<ref name="Olah" /><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Michael E. Jung |author2=Mark A. Lyster | title = Conversion of alkyl carbamates into amines via treatment with trimethylsilyl iodide | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.,_Chem._Commun.|J. Chem. Soc., Chem. Commun.]] |issue=7 | year = 1978 | pages = 315–316 | doi = 10.1039/C39780000315}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Richard S. Lott |author2=Virander S. Chauhan |author3=Charles H. Stammer | title = Trimethylsilyl iodide as a peptide deblocking agent | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.,_Chem._Commun.|J. Chem. Soc., Chem. Commun.]] |issue=11 | year = 1979 | pages = 495–496 | doi = 10.1039/C39790000495}}</ref>并适用于其他脱保护方法不可行的情况下。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Zhijian Liu |author2=Nobuyoshi Yasuda |author3=Michael Simeone |author4=Robert A. Reamer | title = ''N''-Boc Deprotection and Isolation Method for Water-Soluble Zwitterionic Compounds | journal = [[Journal_of_Organic_Chemistry|J. Org. Chem.]] | year = 2014 | volume = 79 |issue=23 | pages = 11792–11796 | doi = 10.1021/jo502319z|pmid=25376704 }}</ref>

